          "text": [
            "For the shapes that rep-tile, what is the <ul><li>Scale factor from the original figure to the image? Explain your reasoning.</li><li>How does the perimeter of the larger figure relate to the perimeter of the original figure?</li><li>How does the area of the larger figure relate to the area of the original figure?</li></ul>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "display": "teacher",
        "id": "6wzAUG20221256AM",
        "title": "Summary of results for rep-tiles",
        "content": {
